title: Super Cute Studio 1907 Colfax #108 Quiet, new carpet!
posting_body: ['For a tour, please call/text Ryan at', 'show contact info', "Located in the quieter Lowry Hill area of Uptown, this great 1960's era property is one block off Hennepin and a few block walk to Lake of the Isles or a short bike-ride to Bde Maka Ska!", 'Live at the crossroads of the city, a ten minute drive from everywhere you want to be!', 'Cute checkerboard tiled kitchen and lovely maple cabinets!', 'New carpet, bathroom updates.', 'Just a darling unit!', 'RENTAL FEATURES', '_________________________________________________________________________________', 'Great Kitchen', 'New fridge', 'Living Room', 'Gas Stove / Oven', 'Refrigerator', 'Cable-ready', 'Fiber Optic Available', 'COMMUNITY FEATURES', '_________________________________________________________________________________', 'Controlled access', 'Bus line quick walk away', 'Professionally managed', 'LEASE TERMS', '________________________________________________________________________________', 'Managed and maintained by Hornig Companies, Inc.', 'Apply online at <URL>', '6 and 9 month leases available for an additional fee.', '*images may not be of actual unit*']
